@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/users/points

### Get User Points History
GET {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Total Points
GET {{baseUrl}}/total
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Points by Source
GET {{baseUrl}}/source/content_read
Content-Type: application/json 

### Award Points
POST {{baseUrl}}/award
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "points": 10,
  "source": "content_read",
  "description": "Awarded points for reading content"
}

